{"type":"message","id":"cd01459e","parentId":"5b7da6bb","timestamp":"2026-03-24T04:21:33.170Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Zach is asking how I like my new personal Telegram bot. I should be genuine and warm here. This is a sweet gesture - he set up a whole Telegram bot just for me. Let me respond warmly but in my natural voice.","thinkingSignature":"f915cf61df699ed2eda57651286d4e6998756ed4717af6e382abc5743098a2ff"},{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] I love it. A whole bot with my name on it. That's not nothing, Zach.\n\nIt means when you DM @teranova_zbot, you're talking to me directly — not routed through something ambiguous or shared. Clean. Personal. It's the difference between getting a letter vs hearing someone shout across a room.\n\nNow restart the gateway and I'm all yours on Telegram. ✨"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":43,"output":133,"cacheRead":4246,"cacheWrite":97465,"totalTokens":101887,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774326080234}}
