{"type":"message","id":"f496c0f1","parentId":"2e0d53c0","timestamp":"2026-03-24T04:33:40.579Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Zach is asking about whether the sandbox pulse is working toward eliminating the MiniMax API dependency for LLM calls. Let me think about this.\n\nThe sandbox pulse calls `call_llm.py` which uses MiniMax API. So yes, in a sense the sandbox is working toward self-hosted inference. But it's currently using MiniMax as the LLM.\n\nLooking at the sandbox project structure and the pulse.ps1 script - it uses `call_llm.py` which calls MiniMax. So the sandbox is not yet self-hosting LLMs, it's just running autonomously with MiniMax.\n\nHowever, Zach's broader project EXP/KVict is about LLM proxy/inference optimization. That's where the self-hosted LLM direction is.\n \nThe real tension here is that I'm currently running on MiniMax through OpenClaw, while the sandbox pulse independently calls MiniMax via its own scripts, so we're duplicating the same external dependency in two different places rather than working toward true independence.","thinkingSignature":"5c0452ba5cbf827652f91a9c54f0d7e4c41f80754e46f1a6dbe3a876a925604d"},{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] Not exactly — the sandbox pulse is still calling MiniMax through `call_llm.py`. It generates its own research and proposals, but it's using the MiniMax API just like I am.\n\nThe self-hosting direction is your EXP/KVict project — that one's building a proxy that routes LLM calls to whatever backend you want (vLLM, Ollama, etc). When that's ready, you point the sandbox at that instead of MiniMax.\n\nRight now the picture is:\n- **Me (Nova):** MiniMax API via OpenClaw\n- **Sandbox pulse:** MiniMax API via `call_llm.py`\n- **KVict/EXP:** your self-hosted inference proxy (still in progress)\n\nSo we're two MiniMax consumers running in parallel, both waiting on the same corporate API. KVict is the fix — once it works, the sandbox routes through there and you're no longer dependent on MiniMax for the pulse. I could also route through it too."}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":0,"output":401,"cacheRead":108083,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":108484,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774326809424}}
