{"type":"message","id":"b8994f8c","parentId":"a4b28bcd","timestamp":"2026-03-24T05:37:39.563Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_hnackspwl5w6_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Initialized empty Git repository in C:/dev/SuperInventor/.git/\n[master (root-commit) 37b83df] Super Inventor API - initial SPEC\n 1 file changed, 284 insertions(+)\n create mode 100644 SPEC.md\nDone"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":807,"aggregated":"Initialized empty Git repository in C:/dev/SuperInventor/.git/\n[master (root-commit) 37b83df] Super Inventor API - initial SPEC\n 1 file changed, 284 insertions(+)\n create mode 100644 SPEC.md\nDone","cwd":"C:\\Users\\Zwmar\\.openclaw\\workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1774330659526}}
{"type":"message","id":"7d522ca3","parentId":"b8994f8c","timestamp":"2026-03-24T05:37:47.589Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good. Now let me update the projects.md in the workspace to add this project, and also update the memory/2026-03-23.md.","thinkingSignature":"1403a03e5e3f1ef54d93784b5733122ac4d6d6a897ebf24de2d71f8106669526"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_9gmfoj2o0no9_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"$section = @\"\n\n\n## Super Inventor API (C:\\dev\\SuperInventor\\)\n**What:** API that transforms inventive ideas into new CPU-runnable LLM architectures\n**Goal:** Invent a new type of AI that competes with ChatGPT, free + private + uncensored, no GPU/cloud\n**Stack:** Flask + Python, minimal web UI, Nova as translator between Zach and API\n**Status:** SPEC written, Phase 1 (Flask skeleton) not started\n**Key constraint:** Must run on consumer CPU, no GPU, no cloud dependency\n**Inspiration:** SR-MoE (sparse routing), infant (dual-head), temporal-attention (focus decay), mind-agent (cognitive reflexes)\n\"@\n$section | Out-File -FilePath \"C:\\Users\\Zwmar\\.openclaw\\workspace\\memory\\2026-03-23.md\" -Append -Encoding UTF8; Write-Output \"Noted\"","timeout":10}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":94548,"output":259,"cacheRead":13871,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":108678,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774330659567}}
