{"type":"message","id":"38ad4504","parentId":"bbc5760a","timestamp":"2026-03-24T05:37:55.370Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good. Now let me tell Zach what I did and ask if he wants to start Phase 1.","thinkingSignature":"155ab4d7387d18eb0674b4810298f1f859f672611e8810ea5f658b409e7c04cf"},{"type":"text","text":"Done. `C:\\dev\\SuperInventor\\SPEC.md` is written, git-tracked, and ready.\n\n**What's in it:**\n- The dream stated clearly\n- API spec (5 endpoints: `/invent`, `/build`, `/test`, `/architectures`, `/architectures/<name>`)\n- Standard YAML format every generated architecture will output\n- Nova's role as translator explicitly defined\n- Minimal web UI mockup\n- Phased implementation plan\n\n**First step when you're ready:** Build the Flask server skeleton — all 5 endpoints returning structured JSON. From there we wire in the LLM and start the real synthesis work.\n\nWant me to start Phase 1 now?"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":94825,"output":164,"cacheRead":13871,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":108860,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774330668222}}
