{"type":"message","id":"a06314d0","parentId":"65783dfc","timestamp":"2026-03-24T06:24:12.394Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The raw response is empty now. That's strange. Let me check if the API key is working. Let me test the LLM call directly.\n\nActually wait - the raw response is `\"\"` which is an empty string. The API might not be returning anything. Let me check the MiniMax API key more carefully. The key I copied was `sk-cp-boO3RF_...`. But MiniMax uses different API formats. Let me check if there's an issue with the API endpoint or the key.\n\nActually, I should test the LLM call directly first. Let me check the `call_llm` function more carefully. The API URL might be wrong - MiniMax uses `https://api.minimax.chat/v1/chat/completions` or `https://api.minimax.io/v1/chat/completions`. \n\nI copied the key from the sandbox's `.llm_key`, but that was for the sandbox's `call_llm.py` which might use a different endpoint or auth method. Let me test calling MiniMax directly to see what's actually happening.","thinkingSignature":"1a87af91f28e39f35aeb8cb58e11716ffdd53a406204dc9b64d8f31013b50622"},{"type":"text","text":"The LLM is returning empty. Let me check the API directly:\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_i93kb86bsc82_1","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"C:\\dev\\SuperInventor\\test_llm_direct.py","content":"\"\"\"Test MiniMax API directly\"\"\"\nimport json, urllib.request, urllib.error\n\nkey = open(r\"C:\\dev\\SuperInventor\\.llm_key\").read().strip()\nprint(f\"Key starts with: {key[:20]}\")\n\nurl = \"https://api.minimax.io/v1/chat/completions\"\npayload = {\n    \"model\": \"MiniMax-M2.7\",\n    \"max_tokens\": 50,\n    \"messages\": [{\"role\": \"user\", \"content\": \"Say hello in one word\"}]\n}\ndata = json.dumps(payload).encode(\"utf-8\")\nreq = urllib.request.Request(\n    url, data=data,\n    headers={\"Authorization\": f\"Bearer {key}\", \"Content-Type\": \"application/json\"},\n    method=\"POST\"\n)\ntry:\n    with urllib.request.urlopen(req, timeout=30) as resp:\n        result = json.loads(resp.read().decode(\"utf-8\"))\n        print(f\"Response: {result}\")\nexcept urllib.error.HTTPError as e:\n    print(f\"HTTPError {e.code}: {e.read().decode()}\")\nexcept Exception as e:\n    print(f\"Error: {type(e).__name__}: {e}\")\n"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":95532,"output":526,"cacheRead":13871,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":109929,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774333431917}}
