{"type":"message","id":"1fcb2e3e","parentId":"e933fda1","timestamp":"2026-03-24T07:47:33.444Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Zach wants a file to store API keys for free API providers that offer credits. Let me think about what free LLM API providers have free tiers:\n\n1. **Groq** - Free tier available, has Mixtral and Llama models\n2. **Together AI** - Free tier with various models\n3. **Anyscale** - Free credits\n4. **OpenRouter** - Free credits, multiple providers\n5. **DeepInfra** - Free tier\n6. **Lepton AI** - Free tier\n7. **Hugging Face Inference API** - Free tier\n8. **Cohere** - Free trial\n\n\n9. **Titan** - Need to verify if this is still active\n10. **OctoAI** - Free credits available\n11. **Replicate** - Free tier for running models\n12. **Modal** - Has free credits for serverless GPU work\n\nNow I'll create a `.api_keys` file with a structured format to store these provider keys.","thinkingSignature":"ad2e5c2ebd4a5101004ee1ba6d4fc644e633725f7bef247a7f1c2794400dd0ca"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_8abmfbz8vbqy_1","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"C:\\dev\\SuperInventor\\.api_keys","content":"# Free LLM API Providers — API Keys\n# Add your keys below. This file is local-only, never commit it.\n# Format: PROVIDER=your_key_here\n\n# ── Groq ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────\n# Free tier: 30 requests/min, Mixtral-8x7b, Llama-3 available\n# https://console.groq.com/keys\n#GROQ_API_KEY=\n\n# ── Together AI ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────\n# Free tier: $5 free credits, Llama-3, Mixtral, Qwen available\n# https://api.together.xyz/settings/api-keys\n#TOGETHER_API_KEY=\n\n# ── OpenRouter ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────\n# Free daily credits, 100+ models from multiple providers\n# https://openrouter.ai/keys\n#OPENROUTER_API_KEY=\n\n# ── DeepInfra ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────\n# Free tier: 1 concurrent, various open models\n# https://deepinfra.com/dash/api_keys\n#DEEPINFRA_API_KEY=\n\n# ── Lepton AI ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────\n# Free tier: 2 concurrent, Mixtral, LLama available\n# https://www.lepton.ai/settings/api\n#LEPTON_API_KEY=\n\n# ── Hugging Face Inference API ─────────────────────────────────────────────────\n# Free tier: rate limited, 30 req/min for inference\n# https://huggingface.co/settings/inference-endpoints\n#HF_API_KEY=\n\n# ── Cohere ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────\n# Free trial: 10M input tokens/month\n# https://dashboard.cohere.com/api-keys\n#COHERE_API_KEY=\n\n# ── OctoAI ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────\n# Free credits: $10, Mixtral, Llama available\n# https://octo.ai/dashboard/api-keys/\n#OCTOAI_API_KEY=\n\n# ── Anyscale ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────\n# Free tier: $10 free credits, Llama, Mixtral, Qwen\n# https://app.anyscale.com/credentials\n#ANYSCALE_API_KEY=\n\n# ── Modal (GPU credits) ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────\n# Free credits for serverless GPU — good for training, not inference\n# https://modal.com/settings/tokens\n#MODAL_API_KEY=\n"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":43,"output":729,"cacheRead":4246,"cacheWrite":107783,"totalTokens":112801,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774338427191}}
